INFORMATION

This file lists changes made to the Ansible role. It follows semantic versioning
guidelines. The content is sorted in reverse chronological order and formatted
to allow easy grepping by scripts.

The fields are:
B: bug
C: change
E: enhancement
F: feature

CHANGES

* Version 0.5.0 (2021-10-15)
C: Add support for OpenBSD 7.0
C: Drop support for OpenBSD 6.9

* Version 0.4.0 (2021-05-02)
C: Add support for OpenBSD 6.9
C: Drop support for OpenBSD 6.8

* Version 0.3.1 (2020-11-29)
B: Adjust return code for monit service check

* Version 0.3.0 (2020-11-29)
F: Add support for Monit service monitoring (suricata_monitor_monit_state)

* Version 0.2.4 (2020-11-20)
B: Fix newsyslog entries (remove comments)
E: Improve newsyslog entries (use pkill command instead of PID file)

* Version 0.2.3 (2020-11-19)
E: Ensure lineinfile tasks can create file if missing

* Version 0.2.2 (2020-11-18)
B: Correct command_cmd_info_suricata variable (only required in remove state)

* Version 0.2.1 (2020-11-18)
B: Correct suricata_flags interface syntax

* Version 0.2.0 (2020-11-18)
F: Add newsyslog entries for log files (eve.json, fast.log, stats.log)
B: Do not reload service in disabled state

* Version 0.1.0 (2020-11-17)
F: Initial release
